---
title: Sweet 'n' Savoury Baked Pork Chops with Mashed Potatoes and Salad
description: This sweet-and-savoury glaze is inspired by the nostalgic "chili" sauce that you can grab from the grocery store shelves. This homemade version is perfect on pork chops and then some! Creamy mashed potatoes and a bright salad rounds out this plate perfect for anyone looking for a little walk down memory lane!
